title: Woodworker's Book of Wooden Toys
description:
Woodworker's Book of Wooden Toys by Vance Studley

English | 1 Aug. 1980 | ISBN: 0442279191 | 116 Pages | PDF | 53 MB

Fifty one of the book's 116 pages are devoted to wood, tools, construction techniques, templates, etc. While all this is very interesting (particulary the history of toys), it is not necessarily of interest to accomplished woodworkers
